1.1.name: wordpress/youtube-videos-widget
1.1.description: Youtube Videos Widget lets you add the latest youtube video anywhere in your Wordpress blog. You can add it to a post or a page with the short code [youtube_videos], or to a sidebar with the included widget. Customize options in the options page and on the widget itself.
